<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Message from Client</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      width: 80%;
      margin: auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #FE705A;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #FE705A;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }

    .client-info {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>New Message from Client</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello Team,</p>
      <p>You have received a new message from a client through the contact form.</p>

      <div class="client-info">
        <p><strong>Name:</strong>
          <%=user.name %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=`mailto:<%=user.email %>`>
            <%=user.email %>
          </a></p>
        <p><strong>Subject:</strong>
          <%=user.subject %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Message:</strong></p>
        <p>
          <%=user.message %>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>Your Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for your attention!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>